{"tid":981341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【尷尬】學警畢業步操蝦碌 甩帽又甩 beat","createTime":"2019-01-14T08:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T01:12:46.000Z","uid":27064,"like":160,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"5f56be3ebd6d20ecf0afe1858ed12e7bc0cf379f","tid":981341,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/01/14/f/ff3fef085c436b9dcd2d822e6e9f4c21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2Ff%2Fff3fef085c436b9dcd2d822e6e9f4c21.jpg&h=54f0433e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為一名學警，最期待的一定是結業禮在一眾親友面前威風凜凜步操的畫面，不過早前網上流傳一段影片，有畢業學警在結業步操上出現「蝦碌」場面，不但警帽跌落，而且跟不上拍子，畫面讓人發笑。<br />\n<br />\n早前一段學警步操的影片於社交平台瘋傳，當時一班學警正在進行步操，從影片可見，其中兩名學警站在最前排位置，帶領身後的同僚前進，其中一名學舉行右手作敬禮姿勢時，不慎撞跌警帽，他立即調整帽子，但整個人卻跟不上拍子，與其他人格格不入，畫面十分滑稽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/01/14/8/88a87f81ad2a1331cb4fab3f51493717.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2F8%2F88a87f81ad2a1331cb4fab3f51493717.jpg&h=4c561fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/01/14/0/048d36ccf4ca7b4ca2bcb8dc176de982.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2F0%2F048d36ccf4ca7b4ca2bcb8dc176de982.jpg&h=9c9d9f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/01/14/2/244c6a42f68dc8a6bfd49c5073005c85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2F2%2F244c6a42f68dc8a6bfd49c5073005c85.jpg&h=87f937e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影片於吸引網民熱烈討論，不少人都表示這段步操影片十分灰諧，也有網民估計這位學警會被上級懲罰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/01/14/9/91290b545e689015b5302fd014978526.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2F9%2F91290b545e689015b5302fd014978526.jpg&h=6c186a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/01/14/e/e42840e1b6eefe81efba2ed38496268e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2Fe%2Fe42840e1b6eefe81efba2ed38496268e.jpg&h=b7293f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/01/14/2/2807e25739e18e0f1c439d2431fb5f43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2F2%2F2807e25739e18e0f1c439d2431fb5f43.jpg&h=270af1b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/01/14/4/4d451b5bd4ce65099a801ea05e6f0e8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2F4%2F4d451b5bd4ce65099a801ea05e6f0e8e.jpg&h=504605b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影片:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chonwa.chan/videos/10216769994149493/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchonwa.chan%2Fvideos%2F10216769994149493%2F&d=6IUnvXXzGGBLGTx%2Bbciszv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=7c6700f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chonwa.chan/videos/10216769994149493/</a>"},{"pid":"74f2667aaa60b64f38c58b9df6c2a465efa2fced","tid":981341,"uid":140769,"like":270,"dislike":2,"score":268,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:41:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb87869682b0dc4a9f15dcdc02a379eb893ea85e","tid":981341,"uid":27064,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78dc35214a459c1dded84bc0d24d6ac99fb76a70","tid":981341,"uid":36901,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0