br />\nBTW.  24:05 全場大嗌&ldquo;pya&rdquo;之後播國歌果下真係好撚型好撚霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"好撚齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f36a907d3e402f23d78aa7f5a63f654b84d6f6","tid":981341,"uid":133375,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a21ddd2c6e80312063b4d9161699e312772f620c","tid":981341,"uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":40,"score":-38,"quote":{"pid":"8b0f0828cc3eeda775d0a70c54894a72ab1075fc","tid":981341,"uid":51200,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"306f0faa6355229648a0366ab923ce12cd1b91dd","tid":981341,"uid":91633,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"內地d紀律部隊呢十幾年跟哂香港紀律部隊d服裝設計<br />\n有時一眼望埋去根本分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"係，交通最似<br />\n之前發夢聽過退役d工具會運上去抄考<br />\n衫/車都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:18:23.000Z","msg":"深圳件衫同香港一樣<br />\n<br />\n香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yEX1M80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyEX1M80.png&h=644bd7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LnTXkt1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnTXkt1.png&h=87556f5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深圳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMESTOO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMESTOO.png&h=630cb034&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:47:56.00